{"tid":2426662,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：數月內或公布立法會改組事宜","createTime":"2021-02-28T08:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T00:02:49.000Z","uid":21470,"like":16,"dislike":204,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"0e92e2bfa332223a826c6e0febdd7726ef14f086","tid":2426662,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:47:12.000Z","msg":"陳弘毅：人大常委會數月內或公布立法會改組<br />\n<br />\n另一與會的基本法委員會委員陳弘毅說，全國人大常委會未來幾個月內，可能公布立法會改組問題，例如涉及直選安排、直選選區劃分、功能組別議席調整、重新分配及設立新功能組別等等。<br />\n<br />\n夏寶龍日前強調，&ldquo;愛國者治港&rdquo;是&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;方針的核心要義，並要抓緊完善選舉制度。回歸後的香港要由愛國者治理，香港特別行政區的政權要掌握在愛國者手中，他並表示堅持&ldquo;愛國者治港&rdquo;是關繫到&ldquo;一國兩制&rdquo;事業興衰成敗的重大原則問題，容不得半點含糊。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2380947\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2380947&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3kyCzF7GSvQxQofikz39bzk%3D&h=d81b8ab0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2380947</a>"},{"pid":"6d3808d69e5ad2ca4feea7e8311e27306e9086ac","tid":2426662,"uid":31773,"like":228,"dislike":3,"score":225,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:48:14.000Z","msg":"你都玩撚爛架啦<br />\n<br />\n你鍾意啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91dfbffc34e0fb07b05938fabd2573658f4b6e33","tid":2426662,"uid":268153,"like":108,"dislike":1,"score":107,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:49:52.000Z","msg":"一國一制啦，仲扮乜？"},{"pid":"ed715cc49c630dd8856301498714c4f589babd89","tid":2426662,"uid":242537,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:55:37.000Z","msg":"弱智<br />\n直接用翠大大個<del>屎眼</del>口做法律咪得囉"},{"pid":"12b7b2ea1ec662c2b2a102ae90f5b367bffebe98","tid":2426662,"uid":100542,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ed715cc49c630dd8856301498714c4f589babd89","tid":2426662,"uid":242537,"like":62,"dislike":1,"score":61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T08:55:37.000Z","msg":"弱智<br />\n直接用翠大大個<del>屎眼</del>口做法律咪得囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02